HEADWORD: Gig
<hw>Gig</hw> <pr>(j⟦icr⟧g <it>or</it> g⟦icr⟧g)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Cf. OF. <ets>gigue</ets>. See <er>Jig</er>, <pos>n.</pos>]</ety>
<def>A fiddle.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
